{"tid":1033134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法國向印太地區部署戴高樂號核動力航母與日本自衛隊聯合演習","createTime":"2019-02-23T01:37:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-23T07:44:20.000Z","uid":28765,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c2283d87833a69f1299d2b17c321a144a73e79e5","tid":1033134,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T01:37:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://gdb.voanews.com/8BE2674E-26C7-47B7-947F-3FFC459B1FD4_w1023_r1_s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgdb.voanews.com%2F8BE2674E-26C7-47B7-947F-3FFC459B1FD4_w1023_r1_s.jpg&h=b3a381d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n法國戰鬥機從戴高樂號航母起飛<br />\n<br />\n法國國防部宣布，將從下個月起向印度洋太平洋地區部署戴高樂號主力核動力航母，其間將與日本自衛隊舉行共同訓練。<br />\n<br />\n法國國防部在星期四的記者會上還宣布，除了戴高樂號航母外，還有3艘驅逐艦、一艘潛艇和一艘補給艦共6艘艦艇將被派往印太海域，為時近5個月。<br />\n<br />\n上個月，法國和日本的外交部長和國防部長在法國城市布雷斯特舉行&ldquo;2+2&rdquo;會談，兩國當時宣布法國的戴高樂號核動力航空母艦駛入印度洋時，日本將派遣驅逐艦參加聯合演習。兩國在會後的聯合聲明中，還對中國在東中國海和南中國海日益增多的活動表示關切，稱兩國&ldquo;反對導致局勢緊張的任何單方面行動&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n此外，鑑於對中國海軍力量的迅速崛起，法國和澳大利亞最近還簽署了一項高達350億美元的巨額軍售合同，在經過多年談判之後，澳大利亞上星期宣布將向法國潛艇製造商&ldquo;海軍集團&rdquo; （Naval Group）訂購12艘潛艇。<br />\n<br />\n法國外交部顧問埃雷拉（Philippe Errera）在接受法新社採訪時說，法國有最大的專屬經濟區，尊重國際法對法國來說不是一個抽象概念。他說：&ldquo;如果海洋法在南中國海得不到尊重，那麼明天在北極、在地中海和印度洋也將同樣被踐踏。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voachinese.com/a/france-indo-pacific-aircraft-carrier-20190222/4799712.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voachinese.com%2Fa%2Ffrance-indo-pacific-aircraft-carrier-20190222%2F4799712.html&d=gMg1FBwAZA1XbJy1Uvmn1HljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=694214f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.voachinese.com/a/france-indo-pacific-aircraft-carrier-20190222/4799712.html</a>"},{"pid":"d2a20b6376e18712af56aab990f1d4b4a3b21fbb","tid":1033134,"uid":18955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T05:00:00.000Z","msg":"好想同啲講法文嘅女軍官瘋狂訓練<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae5dbab6e131d96111b08c884edb37b4aec5917b","tid":1033134,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d2a20b6376e18712af56aab990f1d4b4a3b21fbb","tid":1033134,"uid":18955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T05:00:00.000Z","msg":"好想同啲講法文嘅女軍官瘋狂訓練<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T05:00:50.000Z","msg":"日操夜操<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17e0a2561b43156060ebbe89e39ea631f28e5e5a","tid":1033134,"uid":34666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2a20b6376e18712af56aab990f1d4b4a3b21fbb","tid":1033134,"uid":18955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T05:00:00.000Z","msg":"好想同啲講法文嘅女軍官瘋狂訓練<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T05:02:55.000Z","msg":"又用F/A-18大破Rafale<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dba58d355f140671b6054a3a35b375efbeca069","tid":1033134,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T07:44:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}